[SN]TITLE[SN]
Flat in Derry badly damaged in arson attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The interior of a flat in Londonderry has been extensively damaged in an arson attack.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
There was no-one in the property at Bayview Terrace when the alarm was raised after 22:30 BST on Friday.
A number of residents in adjoining flats had to leave while fire crews worked to put out the fire.
Police have appealed for anyone with information to contact them.
